# Kusur, Republic of Dagestan

}}
Kusur (; ) is a rural locality (a selo) in Kalyalskoye Rural Settlement, Rutulsky District, Republic of Dagestan, Russia. Population:  There are 2 streets.
Geography
Kusur is located 50 km northwest of Rutul (the district's administrative centre) by road.
Nationalities
Avars live there.
